# LLM standards (Python)

- Use **LiteLLM** as the provider layer and **Instructor** for structured outputs.
- All LLM calls must return **validated Pydantic v2 models** (no ad-hoc JSON parsing).
- Include timeouts and handle provider errors gracefully (meaningful errors + structured logs).
- Avoid logging secrets; redact API keys/tokens and sensitive user data in logs.
